  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a saucepan, mix plum jam and tomato sauce.",
    "Add garlic powder, vegan butter, chocolate chips (if using), cocoa powder, vanilla extract, flour, salt, and pepper. Mix well until smooth.",
    "Transfer mixture into an oven-safe baking dish. Bake for 25 minutes or until golden brown on top.",
    "Allow to cool slightly before serving."
